{"tid":155292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地：踢波定踢人呀？","createTime":"2017-03-14T01:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T03:54:46.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72c0e60e92d3c113bbb839c01fdc29bd9bede976","tid":155292,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"周一晚的英足盃8強，車路士翼鋒夏薩特被曼聯球員特別「招呼」，令藍軍領隊干地十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n夏薩特在開賽早段就被到菲爾鍾斯嚴密看管，更令到安達靴里拉領紅。干地表示：「我認為，他們（曼聯）應該要踢足球，而我的球員亦想踢足球。在頭20或25分鐘，夏薩特根本沒可能踢足球，我見到很多被踢的情況。我應該不是瘋的，但我只見到他有這情況。」<br />\n<br />\n干地亦稱讚夏薩特能沉得住氣：「他顯示出人品，很好的人。這是很難，而且很危險，要被人從後踢。」"},{"pid":"ee921faa1ba0f12b2331d2612af22002aa53c330","tid":155292,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"打狗"},{"pid":"34a8fa4c825a9894b0e6c6c82fbfeeca5b4c83ce","tid":155292,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PzAj3knAo_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPzAj3knAo_c&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=de8ee5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PzAj3knAo_c</a><br />\n<br />\n魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5151859578841303b232f8b68921c95d5dc84a","tid":155292,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"沙皮狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a276ce0e807bfca3c1d2331dc5d857cd2a9e59f","tid":155292,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"掂下都唔比 翻去打乒乓波啦"},{"pid":"faebfa50e9166d5b65254223ee63b5470c1b4d9b","tid":155292,"uid":23399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:08:44.000Z","msg":"<b